functions.name: All non-critical topics

functions.name: Motion
functions.description: Side-effect-less proposals to set general governance direction.

functions.description: Proposal to change the core parameters of SNS governance.

functions.name: Upgrade SNS controlled canister
functions.description: Proposal to upgrade the wasm of an SNS controlled canister.

functions.name: Add nervous system function
functions.description: Proposal to add a new, user-defined, nervous system function: a canister call which can then be executed by proposal.

functions.name: Remove nervous system function
functions.description: Proposal to remove a user-defined nervous system function, which will be no longer executable by proposal.

functions.name: Execute nervous system function
functions.description: Proposal to execute a user-defined nervous system function, previously added by an AddNervousSystemFunction proposal. A canister call will be made when executed.
